efore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Elizabeth de Lambersart was born about 1155, in Lambersart, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France, her father, Jean I de Peteghem, was 36 and her mother, Pétronille d'Avesnes, was 26. She married Jean de Nesle in 1175. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 2 daughters. She died in 1224, at the age of 70."},"et":{"environ 1155–1224":"umbes 1155–1224","1155–1224":"1155–1224","–Female":"Surnud","1150–1197":"1150–1197","1175–Female":"1175–Surnud","1179–1229":"1179–1229","1182–1226":"1182–1226","1120–1154":"1120–1154","1130–1186":"1130–1186","environ 1155":"umbes 1155","environ 1175":"umbes 1175","1154":"1154","1175":"1175","1186":"1186","1120":"1120","1197":"1197","environ 1182":"umbes 1182","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","1182":"1182","14 juillet 1197":"14. juuli 1197","1226":"1226","1224":"1224","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1229":"1229","Lambersart, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Lambersart, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa","Brugge, Flandre occidentale, Belgique":"Brugge, West-Vlaanderen, Belgia","Normandie, França":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Nesle, Somme, Picardy, France":"Nesle, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"environ 1155–1224":"noin 1155–1224","1155–1224":"1155–1224","–Female":"Kuollut","1150–1197":"1150–1197","1175–Female":"1175–Kuollut","1179–1229":"1179–1229","1182–1226":"1182–1226","1120–1154":"1120–1154","1130–1186":"1130–1186","environ 1155":"noin 1155","environ 1175":"noin 1175","1154":"1154","1175":"1175","1186":"1186","1120":"1120","1197":"1197","environ 1182":"noin 1182","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","1182":"1182","14 juillet 1197":"14. heinäkuuta 1197","1226":"1226","1224":"1224","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1229":"1229","Lambersart, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Lambersart, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Ransk